{"id": "1508637964014714940", "channel_id": "1505167541818101862", "type": 0, "author_id": "1341353800459485247", "author_name": "somethingno1fan", "author_bot": false, "content": "Guys, I have a HUGE PROBLEM IN MY LIFE. I don't even know what could be worse. My wife left me, and the company I work for went bankrupt. On the same day, I found out that my daughter has five boyfriends. All at the same time. It's like Piper Perri... I think all these misfortunes have fallen upon me because I didn't cry in Discord yesterday... Cancel 300 normal pull for stats?((... I hope things will get better now", "timestamp": "2026-05-26T01:08:39.759000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "Alva_goodjob", "emoji_id": "1468259169965707398", "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1505167541818101862", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.5.1.0 停服维护公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881"}
