{"id": "1508778125847433237", "channel_id": "1505167541818101862", "type": 19, "author_id": "594196021119287316", "author_name": "nemu_s_t_a_r", "author_bot": false, "content": "COOL<:Brown_think:1459080117308620996>\n原來有人看", "timestamp": "2026-05-26T10:25:36.944000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1508618486778298430", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1505167541818101862", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.5.1.0 停服维护公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881"}
{"id": "1508794333384413274", "channel_id": "1505167541818101862", "type": 0, "author_id": "594196021119287316", "author_name": "nemu_s_t_a_r", "author_bot": false, "content": "程序員說「要有倉庫」，Codex 便初始化了 git。這是第一小時\n\n程序員說「代碼之間要有分別，將入口與實現分開」，於是'src'、tests*與 docs 各歸其位。這是第二小時\n\n程序員說「要有接口，使人知道當怎樣使用」，於是類型與契約便顯明出來。這是第三小時。\n\n程序員說「要有測試，分辨可運行的與不可運行的」，於是紅的漸少，綠的漸多。這是第四小時。\n\n傍晚，他與十三個 subagent 同查代碼時，Codex 對他說：\n5-hour limit reached • resets 9pm\n他就停了工。", "timestamp": "2026-05-26T11:30:01.122000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🌿", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1505167541818101862", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.5.1.0 停服维护公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881"}
